lready established your page  you will see it  Begin editing  Click on NEW PAGE and this will toss you right into the Editor  Name your page  Keep it simple and after the name  type  htm    forexample  havana htm Press enter and while the name is still selected  double click and you are ready to begin composing  But first  On your toolbar  click TABLE and INSERT TABLE  When the window appears  size it like this  Row 1  column 1  alignment Center  Border Size 0  width 600  and in pixels  Press TAB a dozen or so times  so that you have several rows  Begin writing inside your rows  Start writing  If you have something already written in MS Word  open the word document and do a cut or copy  paste into your Front Page document  How to link to another page  Compose something to lead your reader to the other site  such as  Click here for  Highlight your words and click on the globe chain combination on your toolbar  right below HELP  You ll see your cursor blinking at the bottom of the box  Type in the URL to which you are linking and type OK  If you are in another page and want to link to it but do not know the address  right click and look at PROPERTIES  You ll see the address  Let s have some fun  COLORS  To select the color for your background  nobody likes an ugly homepage  click FORMAT and background  A window pops up  On the left you will see a box for BACKGROUND colors  In the drop down box  curse down  If you do not like what you see  click on CUSTOM and design your own colors  Move the color wheel up down side side until you see a color in the big box that suits  On the LEFT  click on OK and your background should change  The same will work for your font  Click FORMAT  font  and select your style or color  WARNING  If you choose to keep your text WHITE  nobody can print your page  The letters won t show up  Would you like to see what it looks like so far  On the bottom left of your screen  click on Preview and you will see your work as it will appear online  Once you look at it  click again on NORMAL  and this will take you back to the editor  SAVE YOUR PAGE  Click File and SAVE AS  The Look in Box should contain the class website  Below that  you should see the cadetname folder  Open it  Double click on your name and click OK  Email me your URL and I will link to it  This will get you started  Col  Bulger Barnett Home Courses VMI Spanish Drills Links of Interest Applications   Forms Language Skills VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 